本屆賽事為女子賽事首次於奧運年舉行。[[國際冰球總會|國際冰球總會]]為了促進沒有被邀請參加奧運國家隊伍的競爭水準，決定每年舉辦賽事。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.iihf.com/home-of-hockey/news/news-singleview/browse/7/select_category/21/recap/5130.html |title=New era of women's hockey |accessdate=2014-10-15 |archive-date=2013-09-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921063928/http://www.iihf.com/home-of-hockey/news/news-singleview/browse/7/select_category/21/recap/5130.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 不過沒有舉辦頂級賽，最初[[國際冰球總會|國際冰球總會]]宣布奧運賽事成績最差的將被第一級A組的冠軍取代<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.iihf.com/home-of-hockey/news/news-singleview/recap/8157.html?tx_ttnews%5BbackPid%5D=955&cHash=2b7d779461 |title=Fasel opens 137th IIHF congress |accessdate=2014-10-15 |archive-date=2013-09-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921073943/http://www.iihf.com/home-of-hockey/news/news-singleview/recap/8157.html?tx_ttnews%5BbackPid%5D=955&cHash=2b7d779461 |dead-url=no }}</ref>最後，被改變為兩隊舉行三戰兩勝的賽事來決定下一屆的層級。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.iihf.com/home-of-hockey/news/news-singleview/recap/8387.html?tx_ttnews%5BbackPid%5D=955&cHash=8966747f25 |title=Promotion format defined |accessdate=2014-10-15 |archive-date=2014-02-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140224214858/http://www.iihf.com/home-of-hockey/news/news-singleview/recap/8387.html?tx_ttnews%5BbackPid%5D=955&cHash=8966747f25 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

